Nosferatu: Strength, Stamina, Intelligence, Stealth, Investigation, and Technology.
Banu Haqim: Dexterity, Wits, Perception, Melee, Stealth, and Occult.
Lasombra: Strength, Manipulation, Resolve, Leadership, Intimidation, and Politics.
Brujah: Strength, Dexterity, Charisma, Brawl, Intimidation, and Politics.
Gangrel: Stamina, Strength, Perception, Survival, Animal Ken, and Awareness.
The Ministry: Manipulation, Charisma, Wits, Subterfuge, Persuasion, and Occult.
Ravnos: Dexterity, Manipulation, Wits, Larceny, Streetwise, and Performance.
Hecata: Intelligence, Resolve, Perception, Occult, Medicine, and Academics.
